===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#an [[increase]] in [[size]], [[number]], [[value]], or [[strength]]
#{{biology}} the act of [[growing]], getting [[bigger]] or [[higher]]
#{{biology}} something that [[grow]]s or has [[grown]]
#{{pathology}} an [[abnormal]] [[mass]] such as a [[tumor]]

